-- Delta names board member Anderson as CEO
-- 
-- Tue Aug 21, 2007 5:22pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/21/us-delta-ceo-announcement-idUSWEN059920070821

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Delta Air Lines Inc ( DAL.N ) on Tuesday named board director Richard Anderson as the airline's new chief executive. 

 Anderson, currently an executive at UnitedHealth Group Inc ( UNH.N ), succeeds CEO Gerald Grinstein, 75, who announced his plan to retire last year.